# Key Bindings (Vim-style navigation)
unbind common h
unbind common l
unbind common j
unbind common k
unbind common g
unbind common G
unbind common d
unbind common u
unbind common /
unbind common n
unbind common N
unbind common q
unbind common x
unbind common Enter

# Vim-style navigation
bind common h previous_column
bind common l next_column
bind common j down
bind common k up
bind common g move_first
bind common G move_last
bind common d delete
bind common u undo
bind common / search
bind common n search_next
bind common N search_prev

# Playback controls
bind common x play_pause
bind common q quit
bind common enter play
